title: 'Snowbridge: receipt verification with alloy primitives'
doc:
- audience: Runtime Dev
  description: "The new verifier checks both the root and the exact receipt key (transaction index), aligning with how proofs are generated and preventing proofs that follow a valid hash chain but reference the wrong key."
